s === AuthenticityStatus.Bindings) return 📝;\\n        if (status === AuthenticityStatus.Proof) return ✓;\\n        return null;\\n      }}\\n    /&gt;\\n  );\\n}\\n\",\"title\":\"Using with Picker\",\"titles\":[\"Prove SDK\"]},{\"href\":\"/sdk/prove#notes\",\"html\":\"\\n<ul>\\n<li>Proof generation requires network access to the prover backend</li>\\n<li>The input photo must have a <code>succinct.bindings</code> assertion (created by the Capture SDK)</li>\\n<li>Proof generation typically takes a few seconds</li>\\n<li>The original photo is not modified; a new file is created with the embedded proof</li>\\n</ul>\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/sdk/prove.mdx#notes\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\n\\nProof generation requires network access to the prover backend\\nThe input photo must have a succinct.bindings assertion (created by the Capture SDK)\\nProof generation typically takes a few seconds\\nThe original photo is not modified; a new file is created with the embedded proof\\n\",\"title\":\"Notes\",\"titles\":[\"Prove SDK\"]}]}}"
